query:
SELECT tp.id, tp.userId, tp.approvalStatus, tp.bio, tp.qualifications, u.name, u.email 
FROM tutor_profiles tp 
LEFT JOIN users u ON tp.userId = u.id 
ORDER BY tp.id 
LIMIT 5;

rows.bio: Passionate mathematics educator with over 15 years of experience helping students excel in algebra, calculus, and statistics. I believe every student can master math with the right approach and encouragement.
rows.qualifications: PhD in Mathematics Education, MIT; Master's in Applied Mathematics, Stanford University
rows.name: Dr. Sarah Johnson

rows.bio: Experienced science tutor specializing in physics, chemistry, and biology. I make complex scientific concepts accessible and engaging through real-world examples and hands-on problem solving.
rows.qualifications: MS in Physics, UC Berkeley; BS in Chemistry, UCLA; Certified Science Teacher
rows.name: James Chen

rows.bio: Award-winning English teacher dedicated to developing strong reading, writing, and critical thinking skills. I help students find their voice and express themselves with confidence.
rows.qualifications: MA in English Literature, Columbia University; BA in Creative Writing, NYU; Published Author
rows.name: Emily Rodriguez

rows.bio: Software engineer turned educator with a passion for teaching coding and computer science. I make programming fun and accessible for beginners while challenging advanced students.
rows.qualifications: BS in Computer Science, Carnegie Mellon; 8 years industry experience at Google and Microsoft
rows.name: Michael Park
